platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: 追尋摯愛，踏上漫長的宇宙之旅，併砌動人又心碎的愛情故事。
恋人を取り戻すため、主人公コスモが宇宙を駆け巡るアドベンチャーゲーム。
和太空人一起尋回機器人女友的碎片，拼湊出感人的愛情故事。

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: When young astronaut Kosmo sees his robot girlfriend, Nova, blown to pieces before his eyes, he gallantly sets off across the galaxy to find his beloved’s parts and put her back together. This beautiful and whimsical point-and-click adventure will steal your heart as you visit dozens of kooky planets and encounter everything from alien arcades to robot discos. Each unique world introduces adorable critters, fantastic sights, clever puzzles to solve and tokens of affection to discover. Star-crossed romance has never felt so rewarding.

When young astronaut Kosmo sees his robot girlfriend, Nova, blown to pieces before his eyes, he gallantly sets off across the galaxy to find his beloved’s parts and put her back together. This beautiful and whimsical point-and-click adventure will steal your heart as you visit dozens of kooky planets and encounter everything from alien arcades to robot discos. Each unique world introduces adorable critters, fantastic sights, clever puzzles to solve, and tokens of affection to discover. Star-crossed romance has never felt so rewarding.
カラフルな星々を巡るパズルアドベンチャー「Love You to Bits」。ガールフレンドを救うため、張り巡らされたトリッキーな仕掛けを解いていく。宇宙人が集う酒場や、時間がループする星など、多彩なステージが飽きさせない。徐々に明らかになるロマンチックなストーリー、個性的なキャラクターたちの細やかな動きも魅力的だ。

Dans ce jeu d’aventure et de science-fiction, aidez Kosmo à retrouver l’amour de sa vie, Nova, un robot dont les pièces ont été dispersées sur différentes planètes. Découvrez des mondes magnifiques truffés de clins d’œil à Limbo, Monument Valley et d’autres titres à succès. Love You To Bits est une expérience visuelle pure qui se passe facilement de dialogues et offre des énigmes ingénieuses ainsi que des flashbacks émouvants.
